{"tid":1635732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月4號  觀塘地鐵站起火有可疑","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:30:46.000Z","uid":259493,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dac979d79ef34095cae996bb433e1b1f3007a1a2","tid":1635732,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須收集大量證據 警犬放火  警犬打爛店舖  警犬10月4號在街上唔見人 絕對懷疑去咗打爛港鐵 大量設施<br />\n要政府交出10月4號的 港鐵cctv <br />\n10月4號 點解一個都拉唔到<br />\n10月5,6號就係咁拉<br />\n10月4號 打爆曬後，林鄭一早準備好出嚟演講怪責示威者， 跟7月1號的打爆立法會陰謀一模一樣<br />\n話畀外國傳媒資知，學生打爛地鐵只想市民免費乘坐， 從來沒有宣傳過破壞港鐵列車， 令廣大市民造成不便， 港鐵係運載示威者離開的主要工具，不可能畀示威者破壞至不能運作</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/posts/2404839876430754?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARCSXoKqvRuPhEt5CMx4NiFyiO-j1iLZS3FdrlY40iwaNANxZf7for0MUdaA8ZyBw-jCbCep0VOjk9lh2Vgof9NMC8P-o_MHg4uJw4W34aCfkIflUkKpPceuLXQ6PhWUku-okfYhGjUthzz0baasNh1ipAbFCoMpa94buUz-7vwCybiWXqvNGQMR6iBCfYXBw31UzSUbDVmaQVlgrugP1z0DkSfSHpgb-Kc77JoTXxHN9WKWpdeLxuE01MMQLQ8zb8-n1RZbwbdDcRotMFvDToskhHU7dJk2wuAQJoNtuzx4liYkGBAeAgAaKpFeFdZ_J_cChLY9l2X8kUoa2Ik9_wzjI662&amp;__tn__=K-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudioincendo%2Fposts%2F2404839876430754%3F__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARCSXoKqvRuPhEt5CMx4NiFyiO-j1iLZS3FdrlY40iwaNANxZf7for0MUdaA8ZyBw-jCbCep0VOjk9lh2Vgof9NMC8P-o_MHg4uJw4W34aCfkIflUkKpPceuLXQ6PhWUku-okfYhGjUthzz0baasNh1ipAbFCoMpa94buUz-7vwCybiWXqvNGQMR6iBCfYXBw31UzSUbDVmaQVlgrugP1z0DkSfSHpgb-Kc77JoTXxHN9WKWpdeLxuE01MMQLQ8zb8-n1RZbwbdDcRotMFvDToskhHU7dJk2wuAQJoNtuzx4liYkGBAeAgAaKpFeFdZ_J_cChLY9l2X8kUoa2Ik9_wzjI662%26__tn__%3DK-R&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=b60be2a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/posts/2404839876430754?__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARCSXoKqvRuPhEt5CMx4NiFyiO-j1iLZS3FdrlY40iwaNANxZf7for0MUdaA8ZyBw-jCbCep0VOjk9lh2Vgof9NMC8P-o_MHg4uJw4W34aCfkIflUkKpPceuLXQ6PhWUku-okfYhGjUthzz0baasNh1ipAbFCoMpa94